-4c97-b07b-613847e87f7e-220x132.png","typeData":{"secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316546238/280b7df1-e299-4c97-b07b-613847e87f7e-220x132.png","source":"CCC","photographer":"CCC","altText":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas","height":"132","credit":"CCC/CCC","caption":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas Photograph: CCC","mediaId":"gu-fc-ab94a824-4f6f-4c43-b75c-6328ea09e8ea","width":"220"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316546521/5c64bd15-3d66-4881-9181-6d1621dd7a79-380x228.png","typeData":{"secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316546521/5c64bd15-3d66-4881-9181-6d1621dd7a79-380x228.png","source":"CCC","photographer":"CCC","altText":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas","height":"228","credit":"CCC/CCC","caption":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas Photograph: CCC","mediaId":"gu-fc-ab94a824-4f6f-4c43-b75c-6328ea09e8ea","width":"380"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316546869/6c0930ae-a127-425c-8321-44e68d0bf956-bestSizeAvailable.png","typeData":{"secureFile":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316546869/6c0930ae-a127-425c-8321-44e68d0bf956-bestSizeAvailable.png","source":"CCC","photographer":"CCC","altText":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas","height":"324","credit":"CCC/CCC","caption":"Current costs of low-carbon technologies, relative to unabated gas Photograph: CCC","mediaId":"gu-fc-ab94a824-4f6f-4c43-b75c-6328ea09e8ea","width":"540"}},{"type":"image","file":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2013/5/23/1369316547455/46b2f5bc-a891-45a5-a436-990f8ac92e7a-540x324.png","typeData":{"secureFile":"https: